parent1.code: A whimsical sketch of five brass clockwork robots in the style of fantastical steampunk. They pirouette gracefully on the ornate surface of a colossal pocket watch in the vast depths of space on a starry night, their gears clicking rhythmically, surrounded by shimmering constellations and colorful nebulae.

offspring.code: A vibrant watercolor of three neon-colored jellyfish in the style of abstract expressionism. They undulate gracefully through a kaleidoscopic coral reef in the depths of a bioluminescent ocean at twilight, their tentacles trailing iridescent patterns, surrounded by schools of glowing fish and swaying sea anemones.
